<div>
<p>
<b>Track registering</b><br>
A new feature has been added to ZamiaDroid. Now, it's possible to register tracks using the external libs called My Tracks. It's necessary to install it separately.<br><br>

<b>Instal·lació MyTracks</b><br>
It's possible to install MyTracks using Android Market or with this link: <a href="market://details?id=com.google.android.maps.mytracks">MyTracks</a><br> <br>

<b>Allow external access</b><br>
It's also necessary to allow third apps access into MyTracks. Change the options, going to settings, Settings -> Sharing -> Allow access. (activate Allow Access)<br>
